- Go ahead.

11:57.001 --> 11:58.300
Stop, Toby.

11:58.369 --> 12:00.736
Nurse Julie, may Toby ascend
to the next step?

12:00.805 --> 12:03.139
- Cleared for all steps.
- Thank you.

12:03.207 --> 12:05.598
Nurse Julie, is Toby
medically approved to pull up?

12:05.676 --> 12:07.076
Yes.

12:07.145 --> 12:08.611
Hold tight there, Tobe-ster.

12:08.679 --> 12:10.513
Nurse Julie, permission to pull down?

12:10.581 --> 12:11.981
This is getting ridiculous.

12:12.049 --> 12:13.215
Can I come down now?

12:13.284 --> 12:15.065
Well, you could if it was
up to me, but unfortunately...

12:15.127 --> 12:16.705
Come down, Toby.

12:17.722 --> 12:18.687
Whoa!

12:18.756 --> 12:20.389
Nurse Julie,
can Toby have a sip of water?

12:20.491 --> 12:21.690
Word of warning, he may drown.

12:23.694 --> 12:25.561
Stop being such a jerk, Rick.

12:25.663 --> 12:27.863
