Oh, did it?

13:18.182 --> 13:19.882
Oh, my God. Sorry.

13:19.951 --> 13:21.851
I must have hit it by accident.

13:21.953 --> 13:23.085
Let's go again, Wilma.

13:23.154 --> 13:24.220
Okay.

13:24.288 --> 13:25.855
