♪ Hey, yeah, yeah ♪

13:31.262 --> 13:32.312
♪ I said hey ♪

13:32.337 --> 13:33.829
U-Uh, Lainey?

13:33.898 --> 13:35.097
Why are you speeding up like that?

13:35.166 --> 13:36.665
Oh. Uh, I thought you could keep up.

13:36.767 --> 13:38.400
Let's try it again. Sorry.

13:38.503 --> 13:39.775
♪ And I say ♪

13:39.869 --> 13:42.371
♪ Hey, yeah, yeah ♪

13:43.608 --> 13:45.908
♪ Hey, yeah, yeah ♪

13:45.977 --> 13:47.176
♪ I said hey ♪

13:47.278 --> 13:48.444
Ugh!

13:48.546 --> 13:50.880
♪ What's going on? ♪

13:50.948 --> 13:52.448
What is going on, Lainey?!

13:52.517 --> 13:54.483
I'm just trying to jam, man.

13:54.585 --> 13:57.286
