14:13.237 --> 14:14.703
I could own thunder. You don't know.

14:14.805 --> 14:16.305
Look, I don't have time for this.

14:16.407 --> 14:18.140
I was just trying to help out a friend,

14:18.209 --> 14:20.676
but if you're gonna act like
a child, I am more than happy

14:20.745 --> 14:23.946
to take my dumb, beautiful voice
and go home.

14:24.015 --> 14:26.315
<i>I had only created
more friction with Wilma.</i>

14:26.384 --> 14:27.683
<i>Meanwhile, Glascott was trying to solve</i>

14:27.785 --> 14:28.918
<i>Mellor and Julie's conflict.</i>

14:28.986 --> 14:30.753
Okay, guys, we gotta figure this out.

14:30.821 --> 14:33.122
I can't have you fighting
in front of the students.

14:33.190 --> 14:34.976
Yeah, no fighting. Julie won't allow it.

14:35.001 --> 14:35.968
Get bent, Rambo.

14:35.993 --> 14:39.039
It's obvious your situation
is made more stressful

14:39.094 --> 14:41.030
because you two play too many roles...

14:41.132 --> 14:42.932
coach, nurse,

14:43.000 --> 14:45.034
aunt, man-dating-aunt,

14:45.136 --> 14:47.829
legal guardian,
man-dating-legal-guardian.

14:47.854 --> 14:48.868
It's a lot.

14:48.893 --> 14:51.407
