18:29.639 --> 18:32.407
<i>But as for me, I still owed
someone an apology.</i>

18:32.509 --> 18:33.441
Hey.

18:33.543 --> 18:35.109
Look.

18:35.212 --> 18:36.978
I'm so sorry. For everything.

18:37.047 --> 18:38.479
That's a start.

18:38.582 --> 18:40.415
The truth is...

18:40.517 --> 18:41.883
I was jealous of you.

18:41.985 --> 18:43.651
That's a gimme. No credit for that.

18:43.753 --> 18:46.221
It's just that being the rock
star is a big part of who I am,

18:46.323 --> 18:47.589
