taken it out on you.

18:59.202 --> 19:01.936
Lainey, you have nothing
to feel insecure about.

19:02.005 --> 19:04.672
It took me six years of college
to become a teacher,

19:04.774 --> 19:05.840
and from what I hear,

19:05.942 --> 19:08.042
you just walked in
with barely any training

19:08.111 --> 19:10.511
to be one of the best teachers
here at this school.

19:10.614 --> 19:12.447
Thank you, Wilma.

19:12.515 --> 19:13.882
And I get the jealousy thing.

19:13.950 --> 19:15.483
I mean, I don't know how I'd react

19:15.552 --> 19:19.220
