19:40.076 --> 19:41.609
<i>than you could have ever imagined.</i>

19:41.711 --> 19:44.145
Give it up for the head of
William Penn's music department,

19:44.182 --> 19:46.281
Lainey Lewis!

19:46.383 --> 19:48.416
Come on, rock star! You take it!

19:50.553 --> 19:53.554
♪ And I say hey, yeah, yeah ♪

19:53.657 --> 19:55.523
<i>And suddenly, the hardest things in life</i>

19:55.625 --> 19:56.891
<i>don't seem so scary,</i>

19:56.993 --> 19:58.993
